The paper focuses on software side-channel attacks in cryptographic implementations, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also evaluates popular libraries and applications, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Additionally, the paper discusses countermeasures and strategies to eliminate vulnerabilities, which relates to cyber physical systems (cs.SY) and cryptography (cs.CY).
